Class InvasionTheatreModel

java.lang.Object
model.invasiontheatre.InvasionTheatreModel
public class InvasionTheatreModel extends Object
The model class for the InvasionTheater object. Contains the properties relative to the current game and methods related to it or to a group of object like fightBelligerents().
